high_descs: Turn right, take a few steps, and then turn right towards the fridge.
Open the fridge and take out the potato on the second shelf.
Turn around and walk towards the oven and find the microwave on top of the oven.
Open the microwave, place the potato in it, warm it up, and take the potato out.
Turn right towards the counter, then turn right towards the edge of the counter, turn left towards the wall and then turn right towards the table.
Place the potato on the table in the middle of the lettuce and spatula.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the potato from the fridge to put it on the table.

place the potato in the microwave oven and cook it for five minutes, then take it out.
turn right towards the table and then right towards the dining table.
place the cooked potato on the dining table

high_descs: Take the potato out of the fridge.
Bring the potato over to the microwave above the stove.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Take the potato out of the microwave and bring it over to the round table.
Put the potato down on the table next to the lettuce.
